data.description: Beautiful, turn-key home. Newer exterior paint. In 2019, a new wrought iron stair railing was added, along with new baseboards, a new double entry door, and new interior paint. Kitchen has newer granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. Plenty of kitchen cabinets for storage.  Kitchen also has a separate dining area, along with a bonus family space with a fireplace,  in addition to the main family living space. Vaulted ceilings make the home open and bright. Home has an enclosed sun room that is attached to house is 280 sf(not included in the square footage) with wall unit air conditioner. New water heater purchased March 2023. Three car garage with plenty of parking for your RV or trailer. Backyard has built in metal shed, great for storage.  Close to the 10 and 210 freeways. Close to Mountain Grove Shopping Center and walking distance to Citrus Valley High School. Seller is motivated to sell. This is must see home!
